org.cef.callback

Interface CefNative

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    CefMessageRouterHandler, CefPrintHandler, CefURLRequestClient
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CefClient, CefClientHandler, CefMessageRouterHandlerAdapter, CefNativeAdapter, CefPrintHandlerAdapter 

    public interface CefNative
    The methods of this interface are triggered by the native code to store and get the JNI counterparts of the JCEF implementation.(该接口的方法由本机代码触发，以存储和获取JCEF实现的JNI对应项。)

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      long getNativeRef(java.lang.String identifer)
      Method is called by the native code to get the reference to an previous stored identifier.(方法由本机代码调用，以获取对以前存储的标识符的引用。)
      void setNativeRef(java.lang.String identifer, long nativeRef)
      Method is called by the native code to store a reference to an implemented native JNI counterpart.(方法由本机代码调用，以存储对已实现的本机JNI对应对象的引用。)

    • Method Detail

      • getNativeRef

        long getNativeRef(java.lang.String identifer)
        Method is called by the native code to get the reference to an previous stored identifier.(方法由本机代码调用，以获取对以前存储的标识符的引用。)
        Parameters:
        identifer - The name of the interface class (e.g. CefFocusHandler).(identifier-接口类的名称（例如CefFocusHandler）。)
        Returns:
        The stored reference value of the native code.(存储的本机代码的引用值。)

      • setNativeRef

        void setNativeRef(java.lang.String identifer,
                  long nativeRef)
        Method is called by the native code to store a reference to an implemented native JNI counterpart.(方法由本机代码调用，以存储对已实现的本机JNI对应对象的引用。)
        Parameters:
        identifer - The name of the interface class (e.g. CefFocusHandler).(identifier-接口类的名称（例如CefFocusHandler）。)
        nativeRef - The reference to the native code.(nativeRef-对本机代码的引用。)
